items.headline: How to massively boost your confidence and self esteem, so you exude authority and characteristics that others admire!
objectives_summary: You will learn how to get out of a rut in life, achieve success in work, dealing with guilt, tips for timid people, how to stand up for yourself, 7 ways to delete a painful past, proven calming strategies, 5 steps to a better self-image, the curse of overwhelm in life,  discovering your inner creativity, and how to be fully self-aware. You’ll also learn how to overcome poor confidence levels and how to stop perfectionism controlling you.

Once you learn these confidence techniques contained in this course, you will discover a new life away from the previous one that may have contained shame, shyness, guilt or inadequacy.  You will understand how you can put into practice a host of confidence tips for all sorts of different situations.

This comprehensive video-based course focuses on one of the most important skills any of us can learn in life – confidence.  People who have  mastered this skill can handle anything life throws at them, both in work and at home, and seem to be able to make new friends easily and seem to be comfortable in their own skin.
